            <div class="title">
                Presentation Of The People Bill
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1948-02-17/debates/e8a4b10d-2ecd-404e-bf8f-92c4ea5359ac/RepresentationOfThePeopleMoney" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
