        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I made an intervention just now which I believe, in the light of my experience in this House, of both sides of the House.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b4439853-d23b-4775-b1a7-c28e206a8efe" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
