    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is the hon. Gentleman prepared, in that case, to agree that the Minister of Education, the Chancellor of the Exchequer, and other Members of the Government should be provided with places in the House of Lords?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-63cd8c6b-73ef-4e97-8844-ff4d97ba52a8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-02-17/debates/211265ee-5bce-4854-af04-d08be208b388/PresentationOfThePeopleBill#contribution-63cd8c6b-73ef-4e97-8844-ff4d97ba52a8">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
