        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I hope that the hon. and learned Member will also mention that amongst those who voted for the abolition of the university vote was the right hon. Gentleman the Member for Pembroke (Major Lloyd George). He was, I think, a member of the hon. and learned Member's party, and now sits on the Front Opposition Bench.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f9c7432d-a026-47eb-b9f6-6dc07480ed6d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-02-17/debates/211265ee-5bce-4854-af04-d08be208b388/PresentationOfThePeopleBill#contribution-f9c7432d-a026-47eb-b9f6-6dc07480ed6d">
