                Mr. Churchill
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-ce97411b-7b85-4857-a6ef-d13485bd055b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-02-17/debates/211265ee-5bce-4854-af04-d08be208b388/PresentationOfThePeopleBill#contribution-ce97411b-7b85-4857-a6ef-d13485bd055b">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
