<p class="">This is on the question of the representation of Scotland and Wales.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-eba9cafe-cb8e-43ac-9c56-24ba5c9d605e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
